T02D2915:314b-1: shr'i badzra bi d'a ra na sto tra /
T02D2915:314b-3: dpal do rje rnam par 'joms pa la bstod pa /
T02D2915:314b-4: dpal rdo rje rnam par 'joms pa la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02D2915:314b-5: dus gsum rgyal ba'i yon tan ngang nyid las //
T02D2915:314b-6: thabs mkhas thugs rjes 'gro don mdzad sprul pa //
T02D2915:314b-7: gdug pa 'dul phyir 'jigs pa'i cha lugs can //
T02D2915:314b-8: bcom ldan rdo rjes 'joms la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02D2915:314b-9: gang gi rang bzhin chags sdang rnam bral yang //
T02D2915:314b-10: gdul bya'i dbang gis khro la khro ba dang //
T02D2915:314b-11: 'dod chags can la chags can lar smos pa //
T02D2915:314b-12: byang chub mchog gnas de la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02D2915:314b-13: gang zhig las dang rnam smin mkhyen pa yis //
T02D2915:314b-14: 'gro ba kun dang ji ltar mthun pa yi //
T02D2915:314b-15: gsang sngags rol pa rab tu ston mdzad pa //
T02D2915:314b-16: bsam yas sprul pa mnga' la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02D2915:314b-17: gang zhig sdang dang gdug pa tshar gcad cing //
T02D2915:314b-18: sdig pa'i mtshon cha sna tshogs 'dzin pa'i sku //
T02D2915:314b-19: nyon mongs dug chen rtsad nas gcod mdzad pa'i //
T02D2915:314b-20: sbrul gdug rgyan gyis brgyan la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02D2915:314b-21: bskal ba'i me ltar 'bar ba'i 'od dbus na //
T02D2915:315a-1: stang stabs brkyang bskum tshul bzhugs pa //
T02D2915:315a-2: spyan gyi sdang mig nyi zla 'bar ba yis //
T02D2915:315a-3: bgegs dpung bsreg par mdzad la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02D2915:315a-4: dus mtha'i me ltar gzi brjid 'bar ba'i sku //
T02D2915:315a-5: glog stong 'gyur 'dra khro gnyer mche ba gtsigs //
T02D2915:315a-6: gsung gi nga ro 'brug stong bzhin sgrogs pas //
T02D2915:315a-7: bgegs 'dul khro rgyal gtso la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02D2915:315a-8: dpal rdo rje rnam par 'joms pa la bstod pa
T02D2915:315a-9: slob dpon bram ze ma ni badzras mdzad pa rdzogs
